asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

name: Luce LaFluf
description: Hot to the touch! Luce prefers "top of the shelf" when it comes to men, cocktails and clothing. Occasionally found hanging out at 3rd world island resorts - it's just her way of chillin from the hectic runway modeling career. Not one for the lime light, it's just hard denying her command of a disco ball-dance floor with those flirtatious trademark batting eyes. You can almost read the minds of male onlookers getting sucked into the abyss of late night romance. Favorite shoes are of course 4" spiked little black pumps with sparkling diamond rhinestones.

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle.

name: Professor  Longhare
description:
The Bach of Fluf Rock.  

As a young boy living in New Orleans, Professor LongHare learned the rudiments of music from his mother. He constructed his own instruments and played and danced in the streets for tips.  But when he found an old discarded piano by his house, Professor patched it up and mastered it under the tutelage of such barrelhouse fluf pianists as Sullivan Hop and Kid Stormy Feather.

His first and only hit song was, Hey There Hop Stuff, recorded in 1973. While he enjoyed only limited popularity during his career, his signature piano style, characterized by a rollicking boogie-woogie bass and engaging syncopation, can be heard in the music of such influential figures as Flufs Domino, Dr. Buck, and Kits Toussaint, who called Professor Longhare the Bach of Fluf Rock and Roll. 

It was not until the 2000s, some 30 years into his career, that Professor Longhare attained greater recognition and he continues to be discovered by new fans around the world.

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle.

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

name: The Pacifier
description: From a long line of peacemakers, I have the calming influence of a strong dose of mycelium, mixed with a medium dose of shmetamine, and can stare down the most dangerous situations with the blink of one eye. I lost my other eye during the giant snow avalanche after the wreck when the fluffle were crossing the Crux, up in the Warren of Ice in the North. While protecting fellow Fluf, trapped beneath the snow with my calming powers, dropping those suffocating flufs pulse rates to nearly zero to enable them to stay trapped for hours with little oxygen, this allowed Snow Crash enough time to burn holes to them all with her fire eyes. However, there were some casualties with burnt ears, some burned out eyes including mine, and some burning off flesh. But the pain and wounds was worth saving them all. The air pockets she created helped those trapped to breath. Mycelium Mystics eyes glow purple from the high levels of mycelium in our DNA, and we feel extremely grounded and connected to the universe and all species. We have extraordinary abilities such as strong telepathy between each other, mild telepathy with those without, the ability to alter the mood of others, and the ability to feel when something is going to happen, before it happens. We are seemingly always plugged in to the mycelium network. Some see it as a blessing, while for those all-knowing, it is a sacred guardianship one must master and respect. Some have been lost from overwhelming voices and emotions circulating their minds. Mycelium Mystics are here to protect Fluf World and guide all of the Amethyst Eyes to ensure the fluffle is always happy.
